sc_cat_item.description:
Built with durable steel framework and high-quality ABS & PP plastic
Five functions controlled by crank (Back-rest, Leg-rest, Trendelenburg, Rev. Trendelenburg & Hi-Low)
PP head and foot board are detachable and easy to clean
4 pcs drop-down PP protective railing, controlled by gas spring
Brake pedal is conveniently located below the foot board
sc_cat_item.name: Variable Height Beds
